These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, fanta, mirinda
4 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla, ferret, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola | hot-chocolate | mirinda | fanta |
| Pet        | rat | chinchilla   | frog | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, spy, time-travel, family
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the british##1
3. the british is in an odd position##4
4. the argentine is the person watching drama movies##1
5. the brazilian is on the right of the british##1
6. the argentine is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | drama  | spy  | family |
| Nationality   | mexican    | argentine | british | brazilian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, peach, kiwi, lime
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, fantasy, epic
1. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | lime | kiwi | peach    | kale      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | epic     | drama | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, puzzles, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, trance, soul, funk
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the fan of ambient and the fan of funk##2
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | collecting | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | ambient   | trance    | funk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, reggae, metal, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, japanese, german, polish
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the polish##1
2. the japanese is the fan of soul##1
3. the german is on the right of the fan of country##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
5. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
6. the italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | country    | metal   | soul       |
| Nationality   | italian | polish | german | japanese |

