.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, musical, animation, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, subway, tram
1. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person driving the tram is the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | satire | animation | musical    |
| Transport     | tram | subway  | helicopter     | motorbike |

