.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, accountant, writer, social-worker
4 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the accountant##3
2. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
4. the social-worker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the dressmaker is between the social-worker and the accountant##2
6. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the rabbit is between the dressmaker and the owner of the pony##2
8. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the accountant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | accountant | dressmaker      | social-worker | writer |
| Pet   | cat  | turtle | rabbit    | pony            |

