.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, grapes, lemon, spinach
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird, dog, goat
1. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the bird and the person eating lemon##2
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating lemon is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | spinach | grapes   | kale | lemon |
| Pet    | goat     | bird | chinchilla     | dog  |

