.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, reggae, rock
1. the person drinking tea is the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of rock is between the fan of house and the person drinking sprite##2
4. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | sprite   | tea | water |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | salsa | rock        | house    |

