.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, mirinda, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, skateboarding, rowing
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee   | iced-tea   | cola      | mirinda      |
| Sport      | parkour | skateboarding | rowing | baseball |

