.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cucumber, nectarine, garlic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, pop, dubstep
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
3. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
4. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
5. the person eating nectarine is between the fan of house and the fan of pop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | garlic | cucumber  | nectarine  | plum |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | pop | r&b | house   |

