.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, spy, sports, romance
4 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, lizard, goldfish
1. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | romance | crime | spy |
| Pet           | goldfish     | horse     | lizard   | hedgehog         |

