.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, traveling, fishing, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, handball, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | camping | traveling         | woodworking   | fishing |
| Sport   | handball    | skiing | snowboarding | parkour   |

