.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, chess, video-games, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, snowboarding, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | chess | fishing | video-games    | filmmaking |
| Sport   | biathlon   | snowboarding  | skateboarding | golf     |

