.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, skydiving, singing, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, canadian, egyptian, indian
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
3. the canadian is the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the canadian is between the indian and the egyptian##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games   | singing | drawing | skydiving    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | canadian  | indian     | malaysian |

