.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, tea, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: peach, kiwi, pineapple, lime
1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the person eating lime is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
7. the person eating peach is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | cola    | tea       | almond-milk |
| Food       | kiwi  | pineapple | lime | peach  |

