.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, italian, indian, colombian
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, scooter, boat, quad-bike
1. the mexican is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the indian##1
5. the mexican is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | italian | indian | mexican  | colombian |
| Transport     | van      | boat       | scooter | quad-bike     |

