.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, accountant, teacher, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, boat, bus
1. the accountant is in an even position##4
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the tram is between the dressmaker and the person driving the snowmobile##2
4. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the analyst##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | dressmaker | teacher   | analyst | accountant |
| Transport   | bus          | tram | snowmobile         | boat  |

 